title: Episode 354: Lip Service Unlocked (Feat. Muni Long & Jason Lee)
itunes:title: Episode 354: Lip Service Unlocked (Feat. Muni Long & Jason Lee)
description:
Singer/songwriter. Muni Long and media expert, Jason Lee join Buda & Angela for this weeks episode of Lip Service. Muni Long discusses being used as a girlfriend for her writing abilities, not needing sex all the time when in a marriage, and getting kicked out of VIP at Cardi B's party, while Jason Lee breaks down his media strategy with Wendy Williams, almost getting arrested in Dubai, apologizing to Meg the Stallion, and much more. Enjoy!
